symphony.domain

Class Venue

  • java.lang.Object
    • symphony.domain.Venue

  • public class Venue
extends java.lang.Object
    Venue creates a venue to be used by Concert and Ticket. It makes use of Address, Concert, and Ticket.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors

      Venue(Address location, int seats)
      This constructor sets the mandatory Address and number of seats.
